data.description: Looking for the feel of country living, but still like having quick and convenient access to shopping and restaurants? Look no further!  This beautifully updated traditional home has all  the amenities one could want. From the lovely indoor living space to the wrap around porch and in-ground pool. Wandering through the park like property you will find a huge storage building, detached garage, chicken coop, a nice sized barn and your own small pond. This property is definitely a slice of heaven.  There is so much more to see so schedule your private showing today.
